palettes/artkal_s.json

The color data in palettes/artkal_s.json (Artkal 5mm Midi "S" series) is
derived from the "beadcolors" project by maxcleme, which is distributed under
the MIT License. The RGB values were converted from the upstream CSV
raw/artkal_s.csv into the "#RRGGBB" hex form used by this project; no values
were otherwise modified.

